The Raviz Kadavu is set on the banks of Kerala’s fourth-largest river, the Chaliyar River. The Chaliyar, also known as Chulika River or Beypore River as it nears the sea is the venue of the Chaliyar River Paddle. The Malabar River Festival ranked the largest kayaking competition in Asia is also held along the tributaries of the Chaliyar river.
